	<h1 class="title">改造完纽约之后，布隆伯格的下一个目标是新闻</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Ravi Somaiya</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-27 09:40:51 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/5591/medium/5591.jpg?1436688607" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


